  "subject": "Revert display of maven artifacts to be updated",
  "commit_message": "Revert display of maven artifacts to be updated\n\nThe operation was added to the default lifecycle and consumes a lot of\ntime on each build on the LF infrastructure, more or less depending on\nthe amount of dependencies to be checked.\n\nA project with ~60 dependencies can see an increase of more than an hour\non its verify job with this plugin activated.\n\nThis patch completely reverts the versions-maven-plugin while we're\nlooking either for a way to speed up this plugin or we find an alternative.\n\nChange-Id: I53451d4f3e27e5c8fd07df46b05c1e313af48633\nIssue-Id: INT-121\nSigned-off-by: Anaël Closson <ac2550@intl.att.com>\n",
